Summary: DISK-OVAL WITH ONE FLASHING LIGHT ON BOTTOM AND SMALL LIGHTS AROUND THE OUTSIDE.
divs: Sighting DetailsABRUPTLY AWOKEN BY "FALLING" OUT OF BED. IMMEDIATELY THUOGHT, YOU GUYS MISSED THE BED. THEN SAW A SMALL FLASHING LIGHT BY THE WINDOW AND DECIDED TO INVESTIGATE. THEN I SAW IT,A LARGE DISK SHAPED OBJECT, WITH A FLASHING LIGHT ON THE BOTTOM, AND SMALLER LIGHTS ON THE OUTER EDGES. I REALLY WANTED TO SEE IT AGAIN AND KEPT THINKING COME BACK. IT WAS HEADING WEST ALONG SUPERIOR STREET. HAD THE URGE TO CALL DAUGHTER AND SAY IT WAS COMING HER WAY.
